{"text_id":208496,"tokens":["Graph","ene",","," a"," one","-","atom","-","thick"," planar"," sheet"," of"," carbon",","," is"," a"," unique"," two","-","dimensional"," (","2","D",")"," material"," with"," remarkable"," properties","."," One"," of"," its"," most"," interesting"," properties"," is"," its"," linear"," dispersion"," in"," the"," vicinity"," of"," the"," so","-","called"," Dirac"," points",","," which"," give"," rise"," to"," several"," exotic"," phenomena",","," such"," as"," unusual"," quantum"," Hall"," effects"," and"," high","-","speed"," transport","."," In"," this"," work",","," we"," develop"," a"," general"," elastic"," scattering"," theory"," for"," charge"," carriers"," in"," graphene",","," based"," on"," the"," corresponding"," Dirac"," equation","."," We"," consider"," both"," the"," in","tral","ayer"," and"," the"," inter","layer"," cases","."," In"," particular",","," we"," derive"," formulas"," for"," scattering"," cross"," sections"," for"," arbitrary"," directions"," of"," incidence"," and"," for"," any"," value"," of"," the"," Fermi"," energy","."," Moreover",","," we"," discuss"," how"," to"," obtain"," the"," elastic"," scattering"," matrix"," from"," an"," arbitrary"," potential","."," In"," our"," treatment",","," we"," assume"," that"," the"," Fermi"," energy"," is"," not"," too"," large",","," so"," that"," the"," Born"," approximation"," is"," valid","."," With"," this"," formalism"," at"," hand",","," we"," explore"," the"," possibility"," of"," tailoring"," the"," transport"," properties"," of"," graphene"," through"," elastic"," scattering","."," Specifically",","," we"," explore"," the"," modifications"," that"," occur"," to"," the"," transmission"," probability"," when"," particular"," potentials"," are"," present",","," and"," we"," provide"," guidelines"," for"," the"," implementation"," of"," controllable"," scattering","."," As"," a"," result",","," we"," identify"," the"," regions"," of"," the"," wave","vector","-","space"," plane"," where"," the"," transmission"," is"," almost"," unity"," or"," almost"," zero","."," We"," apply"," our"," general"," theory"," to"," study"," tunneling"," and"," localization"," phenomena","."," In"," this"," regard",","," we"," derive"," approximate"," analytical"," expressions"," for"," the"," localization"," length"," in"," the"," vicinity"," of"," the"," conduction"," and"," valence"," bands","'"," Dirac"," points","."," With"," the"," help"," of"," our"," theory",","," it"," should"," now"," be"," possible"," to"," tailor"," the"," transmission"," properties"," of"," graphene"," through"," elastic"," scattering","."," Such"," tailoring"," may"," find"," applications"," in"," the"," fields"," of"," nanop","hot","onics",","," sensor"," technology",","," and"," nano","electronics","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"dolly","label":1}